        <Parent_String>traveling bags [300215545], luggage [300225937], containers for personal gear [300197584], containers for personal use [300198399], containers by function or context [300197200], containers (receptacles) [300197197], Containers (hierarchy name) [300045611], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
